org.eclipse.modisco.eclipseplugin
Interface EclipsePlugin

public interface EclipsePlugin

A representation of the model object 'Eclipse Plugin'.

The following features are supported:

  • Bundle
  • Java Model
  • Inventory Project
  • Class Path Root
  • Build Properties
  • Plugin Properties
  • Bundle Properties
  • Output Directory
  • Src Directory
  • Name
  • Plugin Xml
  • Project

See Also:
